    </dt>
    <dd>{{% md %}}All Certificates issued by the CertificateAuthority must match at least one listed ReusableConfigWrapper. If a ReusableConfigWrapper has an empty field, any value will be allowed for that field.{{% /md %}}</dd></dl>
